{"tid":847722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公路出九龍14車串燒 至少11人傷","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T11:56:34.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30c7a2a5aa4561f880bc269d7081e077bcf8a30f","tid":847722,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:20:36.000Z","msg":"傍晚6時許，屯門公路出九龍方向近汀九交匯處發生14車相撞意外，意外中至少11人受傷。現場消息指，最前方一輛的士與3輛私家車發生相撞，3人受傷，其後駛至的8輛私家車及1輛的士懷疑收掣不及，同時相撞，再有8人受傷。受事故影響，上址交通嚴重擠塞，龍尾塞至嘉龍村，屯門公路往九龍方向近豪景花園的部份行車線現已封閉，運輸署呼籲駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58756762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58756762&d=fph60a7mJUwJE%2BnUXaOkiYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b44489f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58756762&h=f4aa0c5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58756762</a>"},{"pid":"9dd75dd5facd9ba86326732b04e75478b5da0ca1","tid":847722,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"出九龍是撚旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d972548bb720795742bd16021bca7c67a265f4f8","tid":847722,"uid":89508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾!"},{"pid":"772fbaf0a6209b7e1bbe2cd412f2797ba82510b0","tid":847722,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb211cd86cbf9b5e587cb8e0b6bfcc89d7af27bf","tid":847722,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"的士⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775ca6f2f03d1